entries.femaleVariant: Daaaad... Come on! Just one hot dog! Or at least some Moonchies!
You heard your mom. She already made dinner.
Yeah, sure! Synthrice and scop. Real preem.
How come we never have anything good for a fucking change?
Hey! Watch your language! You can talk that way around your friends, not around me!
Jeez, sorry. Just had enough of that gunk.
Yeah, I know. Just be patient. I'll get a better job soon, we'll all go to Pepper & Spice. OK?
